They say dog is man's best friend. But for me Lulu is my child. For the past six years Lulu has cuddled up on my feet to warm them. Gave me puppy kisses while I cried to cheer me up. Laid in bed with me all day when I was too sick to play. Cleaned up all the food I've dropped in the kitchen while attempting to cook. Barked at nothing at my door to make sure no invisible bad guys get me. She's even trapped me in a car with her very foul gas. This four legged furry human child warms my heart everyday.
